<section class="suds-contact">
  <div class="suds-contact__wrap">
    <p class="suds-contact__eyebrow">Request a mobile detailing quote</p>
    <h1>Tell Sam what your vehicle needs.</h1>
    <p>
      For the most accurate quote, include your vehicle year, make, model, city, and photos of the interior and exterior if possible.
      Sam will recommend the right mobile detail for your vehicle condition, schedule, and goals.
    </p>
    <div class="suds-contact__grid">
      <article>
        <h2>Text</h2>
        <p>Best for quick quotes, photos, and scheduling.</p>
        <a href="sms:+14253618838">(425) 361-8838</a>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h2>Email</h2>
        <p>Best for detailed requests, ceramic coating, or commercial work.</p>
        <a href="mailto:sudsautosalon@gmail.com">sudsautosalon@gmail.com</a>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h2>What to send</h2>
        <p>Vehicle, city, photos if available, problem areas, and whether you want Basic, Signature, Elite Reset, Ceramic, or maintenance.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .suds-contact {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #111111;
  }

  .suds-contact__wrap {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 58px 20px 26px;
  }

  .suds-contact__eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: #8c6b05;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .suds-contact h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(3.8rem, 7vw, 7rem);
    line-height: .95;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .suds-contact h2 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .suds-contact p {
    max-width: 850px;
    color: #292929;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .suds-contact__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }

  .suds-contact article {
    min-height: 170px;
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid #dedede;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #f7f7f7;
  }

  .suds-contact a {
    color: #111111;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 4px;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 900px) {
    .suds-contact__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Suds contact quote",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Suds contact quote"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
